# zcash.school environment variables
# Copy to .env for local dev. In production, set these in the Vercel
# project (Settings -> Environment Variables). NEVER commit a real .env.

# --- /airdrops + /claim submission delivery (src/pages/api/airdrops.ts) ---
#
# Submissions land in the Airdrops Team Google Sheet via a Google Apps
# Script Web App. No Resend, no inbox, no third-party CRM. Setup steps
# live in scripts/airdrops-sheet.gs (5 minutes, one time).
#
# Paste the Apps Script "Web app URL" here after deploying. If unset,
# submissions still succeed for the visitor and are logged to Vercel
# function logs (recoverable). Set it to record directly into the sheet.
AIRDROPS_WEBHOOK_URL=
